text: Donny Donker (born 5 August 1994) is a Dutch martial arts fighter. He represents the Netherlands in ju-jitsu at international competitions. At the 2017 Ju-Jitsu World Championships he won the bronze medal. He competed at the 2022 World Games, winning individually the silver medal in the -85 category and won the bronze medal in the mixed team event. While flying to international competitions when necessary, Donker has a fear of flying. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch martial artists
